---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Meet the MBS Medical team — a military-trained PA-C and two supervising physicians with decades of clinical experience.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-warm-light to-bg py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block text-accent font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">About Us</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-primary-dark mb-6">Built on relationships, not appointments</h1>
      <p class="text-text-light text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        MBS Medical was founded on a simple idea: healthcare works better when your provider actually knows you. One consistent provider, comprehensive records, and a care plan that evolves with your life.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-warm-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3">Continuity of care</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">You see the same provider every time. They know your history, your medications, and your goals — not just what's in the chart.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-warm-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark mb-3">Evolving care plans</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Your care plan isn't static. It grows and adapts as your health changes, your goals shift, and new information comes in.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-warm-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading eyebrow="The Team" title="Who's behind your care" />
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">

        <!-- David -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto bg-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark">David, PA-C</h3>
          <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium mb-4">Physician Associate &middot; Founder</p>
          <ul class="text-text-light text-sm space-y-2 text-left">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> 12 years U.S. Army service</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> PA-C, Licensed in Florida</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> Primary care, weight loss, TRT evaluation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-light text-xs mt-4 leading-relaxed">Founded MBS Medical to provide direct, consistent access to a provider who knows each patient's full health picture.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr. Folkens -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto bg-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark">Dr. Eric Folkens, MD</h3>
          <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium mb-4">Supervising Physician</p>
          <ul class="text-text-light text-sm space-y-2 text-left">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> American Board of Family Medicine certified</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> 34+ years clinical practice</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> Family medicine and primary care</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Dr. Dawson -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-warm-dark/10 shadow-sm text-center">
          <div class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto bg-warm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary/40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-xl text-primary-dark">Dr. Mark Dawson, MD</h3>
          <p class="text-accent text-sm font-medium mb-4">Supervising Physician</p>
          <ul class="text-text-light text-sm space-y-2 text-left">
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> 30+ years clinical practice</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> Gastroenterology and metabolic health</li>
            <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-primary">&#8226;</span> Oversight for GI health and complex cases</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-primary">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-white mb-4">Ready to meet your provider?</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg mb-10">Book a visit and start building a care relationship that lasts.</p>
      <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white text-primary-dark px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full text-base font-semibold hover:bg-warm-light transition-all hover:shadow-lg">
        Book a Visit
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
